<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>비밀번호 찾기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/forgot-password.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main class="container page">
            <section class="forgot-wrap">
                <div class="forgot-box">
                    <p class="forgot-label">ACCOUNT</p>
                    <h2 class="forgot-title">비밀번호 찾기</h2>
                    <p class="forgot-desc">
                        가입한 아이디와 이메일 주소를 모두 입력해 주세요.
                        정보가 일치하면 입력한 이메일로 임시 비밀번호를 발송해 드립니다.
                    </p>

                    <form class="forgot-form" id="forgot-password-form">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="forgot-username">아이디</label>
                            <input type="text" id="forgot-username" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요." />
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="forgot-email">이메일</label>
                            <input type="email" id="forgot-email" placeholder="가입한 이메일을 입력하세요." />
                        </div>

                        <p class="forgot-message" id="forgot-password-message"></p>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary forgot-submit">임시 비밀번호 발송</button>
                    </form>

                    <div class="forgot-links">
                        <a href="/login-page">로그인으로 돌아가기</a>
                        <a href="/register-page">회원가입</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/forgot-password.js"></script>
            <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
